article_text:

article_summary:
A constant of political life has been that there is only one “stupid party” in America—the Republican Party.
In the liberal pundits’ telling, Republicans are the party of the yahoo heartland, the anti-abortion religious right and the anti-government tea party.
The Democrats are turning themselves into the new stupid party of American politics.
Then one day you get out of bed, look out the window and what do you see?
